at\n$\\mathcal{O}_c^0$ is braided tensor equivalent to the\n$PSL(2,\\mathbb{C})$-equivariantization of the category of\n$\\mathcal{W}(p)$-modules.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Nov 2020 08:03:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 2 Apr 2021 01:33:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-05"}
