al and foreground B-modes) $\\sigma(r)=0.015$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Nov 2020 10:32:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 26 Aug 2021 15:18:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-27"}
